OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FTwo investigative journalists have
OL,8,Fcalled for answers ahead of a tribunal
OL,9,Fhearing to examine allegations that
OL,10,Fthey were subject to covert
OL,11,Fsurveillance by UK authorities.
OL,13,FSenior legal figures sitting on the
OL,14,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal are
OL,15,Fhearing a case brought by Northern
OL,16,FIreland-based film-makers Barry
OL,17,FMcCaffrey and Trevor Birney.
