OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FIn 2018, Mr McCaffrey and Mr Birney
OL,8,Frose to public prominence after they
OL,9,Fwere controversially arrested as part
OL,10,Fof a police investigation into the
OL,11,Falleged leaking of a confidential
OL,12,Fdocument that appeared in a
OL,13,Fdocumentary the men made on a Troubles
OL,14,Fmassacre.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/10
