OL,3,CJournalists call for truth ahead of
OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe PSNI, citing a conflict of
OL,8,Finterest, asked Durham Police to lead
OL,9,Fthe investigation into the inclusion
OL,10,Fof the Police Ombudsman for Northern
OL,11,FIreland document in the No Stone
OL,12,FUnturned film on the 1994 UVF massacre
OL,13,Fin Loughinisland, Co Down.
OL,15,FFormer PSNI chief constable Simon
OL,16,FByrne later unreservedly apologised
OL,17,Ffor how the men had been treated and
OL,18,Fthe PSNI agreed to pay #875,000 in
OL,19,Fdamages to the journalists and the
OL,20,Ffilm company behind the documentary.
