OL,3,CJournalists call for truth ahead of
OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe 2020 settlement came after a court
OL,8,Fruled that the warrants used by police
OL,9,Fto search the journalists' homes and
OL,10,FFine Point Films had been
OL,11,F"inappropriate".
OL,13,FIn 2019, Mr Birney and Mr McCaffrey
OL,14,Flodged a complaint with the
OL,15,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal asking
OL,16,Fit to establish whether there had been
OL,17,Fany unlawful surveillance of them.
