OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe respondents in the case are the
OL,8,FPSNI, Durham Police, MI5, the Security
OL,9,FService Government Communications
OL,10,FHeadquarters (GCHQ) and several
OL,11,FGovernment ministers.
OL,13,FIn a two-day hearing at the Royal
OL,14,FCourts of Justice in London, the
OL,15,Ftribunal will also probe a separate
OL,16,Fissue, pre-dating the documentary,
OL,17,Fwhich involves claims that police
OL,18,Fofficers unlawfully accessed Mr
OL,19,FMcCaffrey's phone records.
