OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FMr McCaffrey had been investigating
OL,8,Falleged police corruption around the
OL,9,Ftime his data was said to have been
OL,10,Faccessed by the PSNI in 2013.
OL,12,FMr Birney and Mr McCaffrey were
OL,13,Fgreeted by supporters as they arrived
OL,14,Fat court on Wednesday morning
OL,15,Faccompanied by their solicitors, Niall
OL,16,FMurphy and John Finucane.
OL,18,F"We're here simply to seek the truth,"
OL,19,FMr Birney told reporters outside the
OL,20,FRoyal Courts of Justice.
