OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"We're here to find out exactly what
OL,8,Fwas going on in the years leading up
OL,9,Fto our arrest in 2018. We don't know
OL,10,Fwhat we're going to hear this morning.
OL,11,FWe don't know how this is going to go.
OL,13,F"We don't know if the PSNI and Durham
OL,14,F(Constabulary) are going to come clean
OL,15,Fand tell us what actions they were
OL,16,Ftaking against journalists in Belfast
OL,17,Fover the last 10 years."
