OL,4,Chearing on state covert surveillance
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"And we need answers today. We need
OL,8,Fthe courts and the police to tell us
OL,9,Fexactly what they've done. Society
OL,10,Fneeds to know that journalists aren't
OL,11,Fbeing targeted by police."
OL,13,FLord Justice Singh, Lady Carmichael
OL,14,Fand senior barrister Stephen Shaw KC
OL,15,Fare sitting on the tribunal for the
OL,16,Fhearing. It was later adjourned due to
OL,17,Flate disclosure of police documents.
